data.jd_text:
**Job Responsibilities** 










 1\. Oversee the Chairman of the Board's schedule, meetings, and travel arrangements, demonstrating a high degree of time sensitivity and organizational skills;










 2\. Draft high\-quality letters, reports, speeches, and other important documents;










 3\. Liaise with senior management, functional departments, and external partners to ensure efficient information transmission and orderly work progress;










 4\. Track the implementation of Board resolutions, urge their implementation, and provide regular feedback to ensure effective task execution.










**Job Requirements** 










 1\. Familiar with corporate business practices and possess relevant knowledge of corporate management;










 2\. At least three years of experience working entirely in English and at least seven years of outstanding work experience;










 3\. Strong coordination and management skills, writing ability, and entrepreneurial spirit;










 4\. Fluent in both English and Chinese, able to use them as working languages;










 5\. Based in Dubai, able to adapt to frequent international business trips;










 6\. Physically healthy and energetic.
